\begin_layout Standard
In this work, we investigate how galaxy bias affects the shift of the BAO
 peak before and after reconstruction.
 A similar study is done by Ref.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "mehta2011"

\end_inset

