reference "eq:model2"

\end_inset

).
 The best-fit non-linear parameter is measured through the fitting method
 described in Sec.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "sub:fitting"

\end_inset

.
 To do that, we treat the non-linear parameter, 
\begin_inset Formula $\Sigma_{{\rm }}$
\end_inset

, as a free parameter.
