\begin_layout Standard
In this study, we present the effects of galaxy bias on the BAO measurements
 using high-resolution N-body simulations with the volume of 
\begin_inset Formula $256(h^{-1}{\rm Gpc})^{3}$
\end_inset

 at 
\begin_inset Formula $z=0.15$
\end_inset

, which is a lower redshift than the redshift tested in Ref.
 
